<HEADLINE> French Gov't Promises Full Investment in Land Arms Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 29 (Xinhua) -- The French government Wednesday
promised to make full investments in the country's land arms
industry.
</P>
<P>
