<TEXT>
<P>
MOGADISHU, April 29 (Xinhua) -- Intellectuals, politicians and
elders from the Habar Gidir clan of Hussein Mohamed Aidid
Wednesday appealed to the warring parties of Southern Somalia to
withdraw their forces.
