<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, April 29 (Xinhua) -- Vice President Al Gore on
Wednesday left for the Middle East both for the celebrations of
50th anniversary of Israel's establishment and for talks aimed at
finding ways to revive the deadlocked peace process in the region.
</P>
<P>
