operating funds, technology, technicians and new operational
mechanisms.
</P>
<P>
Small- to medium-sized ventures account for 94 percent of
Heilongjiang's total 3,538 state-owned enterprises involved in the
machine-building, metallurgy, light industry, textile, chemical,
pharmaceutical and building materials sectors. 
