<HEADLINE> Shanghai Promotes Cooperation with Inland Areas </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, April 30 (Xinhua) -- East China's Shanghai
municipality, the nation's leading industrial and commercial
centers, has extensively promoted cooperation with other parts of
the country.
</P>
<P>
Statistics for the past two years show that Shanghai's
industrial sector has invested in 155 projects in other parts of
the country, with total investment approaching three billion
yuan. In addition, the city's commercial sector invested 4.9
billion yuan in some 500 projects outside Shanghai.
</P>
