<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, April 29 (Xinhua) -- Brazilian Fernando Meligeni,
ranked just 77th in the world, stunned second-seeded Russian
Yevgeny Kafelnikov 6-4, 6-4 in the second-round of the ATP Tour
event here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Kafelnikov, ranked sixth in the world, was fragile on service
and Meligeni got the only break of the first set to win it in just
37 minutes.
